    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, always kept in the garage and pampered like one of the family. Honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
