    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that must be seen to be fully appreciated. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a day of inclement weather. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings; it has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating applied just six months ago. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from the day it left the showroom. The premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the original floor mats are pristine. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a folder of comprehensive service records documenting every scheduled maintenance interval performed exclusively at the dealership. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows zero signs of corrosion. It sits on a set of matching high-performance tires with over 90% tread remaining. This is a rare opportunity to own a turnkey, showroom-quality example for the discerning enthusiast who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
