    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2004 BMW M3 Coupe featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band peaking at an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. This example is mechanically sorted with documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan Systems components. The chassis has been enhanced with proactive rear subframe reinforcement plates to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The exterior retains its factory luster with no clear coat failure, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. A turn-key, investment-grade driver's car.",
